quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  44,19,"Ne mulakholela Nyasaye obufuru tawe. Toto esie ndalabarerera ebifune biyela."
  44,20,"Ne esie ndiliinda khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi khandi Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi mulandasa amachina tawe."
  44,21,"Ne nimulasuubila tawe, be ehale ninasi.”"
  44,22,"Nasaba Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mbu: “Toto bano ni Abandu abamabii.”"
  44,23,"Mana Nyasaye naboola mbu: “Rula nende Abasumba banje eshilo. Toto enywe mulalondwakhwo."
  44,24,"Ne oleshe inyanza endio ngayilekhaane. Toto abo ni omukanda kweliyie kwitsa okhusishibwa.”"
  44,25,"Ne balekha emikunda chinga nende tsisebele?"
  44,26,"Nende emimela nende obwami bwoluyali."
  44,27,"Nende obwokholo bwabasangalilanga."
  44,28,"Endio nilwa kali, mana nikhuhelesia ako Abandu bandi."
  44,29,"Ne likulu nohomba eshialo shibialila khulwa bo tawe, ne shibahebwa ebise tawe."
  44,30,"Ne toto khwahabina Abana ba Israili okhurulana nende eshinyasio shiokhubatutuyia."
  44,31,"Okhurulana nende Firauni, toto ye yali Omufuru mubalia babura eshichelo."
  44,32,"Ne toto khwabalobola khumachesi kefu, okhushila ebilonje bindi bioosi."
  44,33,"Ne nikhubahelesia ebimanyisio biefu, amatemo kalolekha."
  44,34,"Toto bano baboolanga mbu:"
  44,35,"“Khubulaho okhufwa khundi tawe halali okhufwa khweimbeli sa, ne efwe shikhulilamusibwa tawe."
  44,36,"Mana lamusiekhwo basefwe nikali mbu muboolanga habwene.”"
  44,37,"Koo, abo naabalayi muno nohomba Abandu ba Tuba’ nende balia baliho imbeli wabu bakhwasishia? Toto abo bali abamabii."
  44,38,"Ne efwe shikhwaloonga likulu nende bioosi bilimwo khumubayo tawe."
  44,39,"Shikhwabiloonga tawe halali khubwatoto, ne abaanji mubo shibamanyile tawe."